<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 12:19:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>克里：特朗普无法阻止绿色能源革命，但中国煤炭威胁迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/kerry-trump-cant-stop-green-energy-revolution-china-coal-threat-looms-2024-02-13/</link><description>美国总统气候特使约翰·克里周二在国际能源机构部长级会议上表示，连任的唐纳德·特朗普不会停止可再生能源部署，但可能会扭转反煤炭外交努力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 12:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/kerry-trump-cant-stop-green-energy-revolution-china-coal-threat-looms-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日经指数和纳斯达克指数创纪录，CPI 潜伏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-13/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 11:15:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：印度IT部担心在智能手机出口竞赛中输给中国和越南</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/india-it-ministry-fears-losing-out-china-vietnam-smartphone-exports-race-2024-02-13/</link><description>印度信息技术部副部长​​在路透社看到的政府文件中表示，印度在寻求成为主要智能手机出口中心时面临着输给中国和越南的风险，必须“迅速采取行动”以较低关税吸引全球企业。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/india-it-ministry-fears-losing-out-china-vietnam-smartphone-exports-race-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚贸易部长要求中国解除壁垒，质疑王判刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-trade-minister-ask-china-lift-barriers-query-wang-sentence-2024-02-13/</link><description>澳大利亚贸易部长周二表示，他将于本月在阿布扎比举行的世界贸易组织会议上与中国贸易部长会面，并推动取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒、龙虾和肉类的进口限制。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:20:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-trade-minister-ask-china-lift-barriers-query-wang-sentence-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>领先军事研究中心表示，俄罗斯在乌克兰损失 3000 辆坦克后依赖旧库存</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-relying-old-stocks-after-losing-3000-tanks-ukraine-leading-military-2024-02-13/</link><description>一家领先的研究中心周二表示，俄罗斯在入侵乌克兰期间损失了 3000 多辆坦克，相当于其战前的全部现役坦克库存，但仍储备有足够的低质量装甲车供多年替换。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:12:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-relying-old-stocks-after-losing-3000-tanks-ukraine-leading-military-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>去年法国葡萄酒和烈酒出口因美国宿醉而下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-wine-spirit-exports-fell-last-year-us-hangover-2024-02-13/</link><description>行业组织 FEVS 表示，去年法国葡萄酒和烈酒出口量从新冠疫情后的峰值下降，原因是通货膨胀削弱了消费者需求，而且利润丰厚的美国市场的经销商清理了现有库存。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 09:32:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-wine-spirit-exports-fell-last-year-us-hangover-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>看涨投资者自 2022 年 4 月以来首次放弃衰退预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/investors-drop-recession-bets-first-time-since-april-2022-2024-02-13/</link><description>美国银行周二的一项调查显示，随着对基础经济弹性的信心增强，全球投资者本月处于两年来最乐观的状态，不再预期经济会出现衰退。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 07:17:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/investors-drop-recession-bets-first-time-since-april-2022-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>图瓦卢选举结果推迟凸显气候影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/delayed-tuvalu-election-result-highlights-climate-impacts-2024-02-13/</link><description>图瓦卢的选举结果被推迟两周，因为危险的天气导致船只无法将新议员带到首都投票选举总理，这凸显了为什么气候变化是这个太平洋岛国的首要政治问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 03:38:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/delayed-tuvalu-election-result-highlights-climate-impacts-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>印度在MSCI关键指数中缩小与中国的差距，权重再创新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-weightage-climbs-record-high-msci-global-standard-index-2024-02-13/</link><description>在最新修订后，印度在摩根士丹利资本国际全球标准指数（该指数为投资者追踪新兴市场股票）中缩小了与中国的差距。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 02:40:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-weightage-climbs-record-high-msci-global-standard-index-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>在关键通胀数据公布之前，日本股市表现优于欧洲和美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-13/</link><description>日本股市周二触及 34 年来的最高点，而欧洲股市和标准普尔 500 指数期货则下跌，因投资者等待可能影响美联储政策的美国通胀报告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 02:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>就业数据公布后美元逼近150日元英镑上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-nears-150-yen-ahead-us-inflation-test-bitcoin-buoyant-2024-02-13/</link><description>周二，在美国通胀关键数据公布之前，日元跌至接近 150 美元兑 150 美元的心理水平，而在强于预期的工资数据后，英镑兑欧元升至近六个月高位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 01:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-nears-150-yen-ahead-us-inflation-test-bitcoin-buoyant-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：日元兑美元接近 150 十字路口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-02-12/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 21:57:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>沃伦·巴菲特 Squishmallows 的制造商 Build-A-Bear 在法庭上对峙</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/build-a-bear-maker-warren-buffetts-squishmallows-face-off-court-2024-02-12/</link><description>沃伦·巴菲特正在挑战“Build-A-Bear”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 20:59:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/build-a-bear-maker-warren-buffetts-squishmallows-face-off-court-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员呼吁对中国药明康德生物技术公司实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-lawmakers-call-sanctions-chinas-wuxi-apptec-biotech-firm-2024-02-12/</link><description>两党议员周一告诉拜登政府高级官员，美国应审查中国生物技术公司药明康德及其附属公司药明生物的制裁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 19:53:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-lawmakers-call-sanctions-chinas-wuxi-apptec-biotech-firm-2024-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>民主党参议员对拜登竞选加入 TikTok 的决定表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/democratic-senator-raises-concerns-about-biden-campaign-decision-join-tiktok-2024-02-12/</link><description>参议院情报委员会主席周一表示，他对乔·拜登总统竞选团队加入短视频应用 TikTok 的决定感到担忧，而白宫表示，政府对国家安全的担忧没有任何改变。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 19:53:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/democratic-senator-raises-concerns-about-biden-campaign-decision-join-tiktok-2024-02-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>